<title>USA: Hambrecht &amp; Quist names Patrick Allen CFO.</title>
<headline>Hambrecht &amp; Quist names Patrick Allen CFO.</headline>
<dateline>SAN FRANCISCO 1996-09-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Hambrecht &amp; Quist Inc said it has named Patrick Allen to replace Raymond Minehan, who will resign to pursue other interests, effective Sept. 30.</p>
<p>The company also has named David McAuliffe, currently co-director of Investment Banking, to the additional, newly-created post of chief administrative officer.</p>
<p>The moves come less than a month after the investment banking firm's initial public offering on August 9.</p>
